# Root Git Ignore for Momentum Workspace

# Ignore Gradle and build artifacts in any subproject
**/.gradle/
**/build/
**/out/

# Ignore IDE configurations
**/.idea/
**/*.iml
**/*.iws
**/*.ipr
**/.vscode/
**/bin/

# Ignore OS-specific files
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db

# Ignore logs
/**/*.log
**/logs/

# Ignore environment/secret files
**/.env
**/.env.*
